o.com/files/174891552/thumbnail_80.jpg","landscape_url":"https://0.s3.envato.com/files/174891554/inline-banner.jpg"},"live_site":{"url":"http://codecanyon.net/item/heroes-assemble-team-showcase-wordpress-plugin/full_screen_preview/11469747"},"landscape_preview":{"landscape_url":"https://0.s3.envato.com/files/174891554/inline-banner.jpg"}},"attributes":[{"name":"compatible-browsers","value":["IE10","IE11","Firefox","Safari","Opera","Chrome"]},{"name":"compatible-software","value":["WordPress 4.4.2","WordPress 4.4.1","WordPress 4.4","WordPress 4.3.1","WordPress 4.3","WordPress 4.2"]},{"name":"compatible-with","value":["Layers WP"]},{"name":"demo-url","value":"http://heroesassemble.smashingadvantage.com/"},{"name":"high-resolution","value":"No"},{"name":"source-files-included","value":["JavaScript JS","CSS","PHP"]},{"name":"video-preview-resolution","value":null}],"tags":["layers","layers addon","layers extension","layers wp","team","team builder","team directory","team gallery","team grid","team list","team member","team members","team plugin","team profile","team showcase"]},{"id":15674168,"name":"QT Places: Interactive Responsive Google Maps Wordpress Plugin","description":"QT Places: Plugin Description\\nQT Places is an elegant and versatile Wordpress plugin to display custom Google maps.\\n\\n\\tAfter the installation, a new post type called &#8220;Places&#8221; will appear in your WordPress menu, and you can immediately start adding new places.\\n\\n\\nPlaces categories\\nPlaces have their own taxonomy, called &#8220;Place Category&#8221;. With this feature, you can easily create maps to display only one or few selected categories of places.\\n\\nUnlimited versatility\\nYou can add Map capabilities to any existing post type, including normal posts, pages, or any custom post type added by other themes or plugins.\\n\\n\\tYou can also use any other existing taxonomy to create the map filters, and to display specific selected categories ","description_html":"<h2 id=\\"item-description__qt-places-plugin-description\\">QT Places: Plugin Description</h2>\\nQT Places is an elegant and versatile Wordpress plugin to display custom Google maps.\\n\\n\\t<p>After the installation, a new post type called &#8220;Places&#8221; will appear in your WordPress menu, and you can immediately start adding new places.</p>\\n\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__places-categories\\">Places categories</h2>\\nPlaces have their own taxonomy, called &#8220;Place Category&#8221;. With this feature, you can easily create maps to display only one or few selected categories of places.\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__unlimited-versatility\\">Unlimited versatility</h2>\\nYou can add Map capabilities to any existing post type, including normal posts, pages, or any custom post type added by other themes or plugins.\\n\\n\\t<p>You can also use any other existing taxonomy to create the map filters, and to display specific selected categories of posts.</p>\\n\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__usage-inspiration\\">Usage inspiration:</h2>\\nFor example, you can create a map of your travel articles, and use the blog categories as filters: for the visitors will be easy and fast to browse your articles based on the country or city.\\n\\n\\t<p>Or for instance, for your site of recipes, you can create a world or country map with the recipes of each region, and use the ingredients as filters.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\t<p>Another useful example, is a map of all the shops of a big franchise, allowing the customer to easily find the closest sales point.</p>\\n\\n\\n\\t<p>Or, you can do all these things at the same time!</p>\\n\\n\\n\\t<p>Instead, you can have in the same page a map of places, a map of posts, and a map of pages or portfolios.</p>\\n\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__super-responsive\\">Super responsive</h2>\\nTested on iPhone and Android, you can also specify a custom height for the mobile version.\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__easy-shortcode-button\\">Easy shortcode button</h2>\\n\\n\\t<p><img src=\\"http://qantumthemes.com/demo/qtplaces/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/editor.jpg\\" /></p>\\n\\n\\n\\t<p>Create maps of every post type you want\\nYou can add map capabilities to any existing post type, standard like posts or pages, or &#8220;custom&#8221; like portfolio. In the following example you can see a map displaying the custom post type Portfolio. Very useful for example for a building company, a shop franchise, a worldwide recipes map, a tour guide, a tourism blog, a travel agency and more!</p>\\n\\n\\n<h2 id=\\"item-description__discover-more\\">Discover more:</h2>\\n<ul>\\n<li><a href=\\"http://qantumthemes.com/demo/qtplaces/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">QT Places Plugin Demo</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\"http://qantumthemes.com/demo/qtplaces/installation/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Installation</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\"http://qantumthemes.com/demo/qtplaces/custom-post-type/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Custom type example maps</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\"http://qantumthemes.com/demo/qtplaces/translation/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Translating the plugin</a></li>\\n<li><a href=\\"http://www.qantumthemes.com/helpdesk/forums/forum/qt-maps/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">Support</a></li>\\n</ul>","site":"codecanyon.net","classification":"wordpress/media","classification_url":"http://codecanyon.net/category/wordpress/media","price_cents":1600,"number_of_sales":12,"author_username":"QantumThemes","author_url":"http://codecanyon.net/user/QantumThemes","author_image":"https://0.s3.envato.com/files/47164967/qantumthemes-quadrato-80.png","url":"http://codecanyon.net/item/qt-places-interactive-responsive-google-maps-wordpress-plugin/15674168","summary":"High Resolution: Yes, Compatible Browsers: IE9, IE10, IE11, Firefox, Safari, Opera, Chrome, Edge, Compatible With: Layers WP, WPML, BuddyPress 2.3.x, iThemes Exchange 1.10.x, WooCommerce 2.5, Jigoshop 1.17.x, bbPress 2.5.x, Easy Digital Downloads 2.4.x, Visual Composer 4.7.x, Cornerstone, Bootstrap 3.x, Foundation 6, Foundat