http://static.pantherius.com/brand/s3.png\\" /></a><a href=\\"http://codecanyon.net/user/pantherius#contact\\"><img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/brand/s4.png\\" /></a><a href=\\"http://codecanyon.net/feeds/users/pantherius.atom\\"><img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/brand/s5.png\\" /></a>\\n</p><h3 id=\\"item-description__\\">\\n</h3><p><a href=\\"http://enva.to/2Hhv8\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\"><img src=\\"http://all-marketplaces.s3.amazonaws.com/growth/layers/landing-badge-small.png\\" /></a></p>\\n\\n\\n<p>Royal Quotes is a Testimonials Grid WordPress Plugin, compatible with <a href=\\"http://www.layerswp.com/\\" rel=\\"nofollow\\">WordPress Layers Site Builder</a>. Display modern, well-styled testimonials with flexible layouts on your website.</p>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__use-it-as-a-standalone-wordpress-plugin\\">Use it as a Standalone WordPress Plugin</h3>\\n<p>However, Royal Quotes compatible with Layers, you can use it as a standalone WordPress Plugin with any Theme.\\n<br /><br />\\nProvides unlimited testimonials in a Grid layout with more than 20 000 display combinations, including style, position and hover animations. Using CSS3 animations, it is compatible with all major browsers and offers responsive display to ensure the best performance on any devices. Trust is the essential part of the successful website, Royal Quotes helps you to increase the quality of your service with a modest and attention grabber manner.</p>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__grid-layout\\">Grid Layout</h3>\\n<img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/royal-quotes/testimonials_quote1.png\\" />\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__different-images-styles\\">Different Images Styles</h3>\\n<img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/royal-quotes/testimonials_quote_different_image_styles.png\\" />\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__fullwidth-testimonials\\">Fullwidth Testimonials</h3>\\n<img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/royal-quotes/testimonials_fullwidth_quote.png\\" />\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__portrait-based-quotes\\">Portrait-based Quotes</h3>\\n<img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/royal-quotes/testimonials_portrait_based_layout.png\\" />\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__unique-image-filter-effects\\">Unique Image Filter Effects</h3>\\n<img src=\\"http://static.pantherius.com/royal-quotes/testimonials_image_filter_effects.png\\" />\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__key-features\\">Key Features</h3>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Boxed and Fullwidth Section Layouts</li>\\n<li>Responsive, Compatible with all major browsers</li>\\n<li>650+ Google Fonts, custom font styles for the quote elements</li>\\n<li>CSS3 Testimonials Hover Animations</li>\\n<li>Custom predefined templates</li>\\n<li>Support single and double quotation marks, hidden arrows, custom border radius</li>\\n<li>Background color or image for the whole testimonial section or for a single quote element</li>\\n<li>Ability to add your own custom CSS code for advanced customization</li>\\n<li>Various Photo Styles, Positions, Vertical and Horizontal Aligns</li>\\n<li>Custom Image Inner and Outer Borders</li>\\n<li>Unlimited Quotes</li>\\n<li>Third, Half and Full Width Testimonials Layouts</li>\\n<li>Ability to add Author Name, Description and Link to the Testimonials</li>\\n<li>translation ready, supports WPML (Standard WordPress Localization)</li>\\n<li>detailed documentation</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__changelog\\">Changelog</h3>\\n<strong>Version 1.1</strong>\\n<ul>\\n<li>minor improvements on images&#8217; style in testimonials</li>\\n<li>added functionality to <strong>use it as a standalone WordPress Plugin</strong> without Layers</li>\\n<li>updated documentation</li>\\n</ul>\\n\\n<h3 id=\\"item-description__support\\">Support</h3>\\n<p>If you have any question or feedback, please feel free to email me via my user page <a href=\\"http://codecanyon.net/user/pantherius#contact\\">contact form</a>. You can also check the <a href=\\"http://support.pantherius.com/